Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉卡修陛下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.17,0:00:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護六英雄之一妮絲的孫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中出現邪惡的怪物阻擋去路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.99,0:00:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不會認輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.84,0:00:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是佛雷姆國的騎士\N史派克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為劇情是這樣發展的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使說是為了取得騎士資格\N還真乏味哪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，腳邊危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.18,0:00:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.12,0:00:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，上方!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.80,0:00:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，這蛋糕做的真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰!佈下這種陷阱害我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.73,0:01:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃，可以感覺到\N製作者的用心良苦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.67,0:01:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，這是黑暗妖精的甜蜜陷阱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.28,0:01:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿，被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.08,0:01:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜歡甜食的暗妖精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢做這種陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要平安無事出森林的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乖乖把餅乾交上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就用點心陷阱\N砸到你說不出話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼大話，我要討回公道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.26,0:01:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何，認輸了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.87,0:01:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就開始試吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.57,0:01:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.71,0:01:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火候是餅乾的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.71,0:01:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種味道就在囂張\N還差的遠呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.42,0:01:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去重做吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是瑪法的指引…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.99,0:01:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了?…為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看哦
